Author:  Stephen Dunn
Project: Monte Carlo Pi
-------------

You need to install the Python (2.7+) and the PyGame library to run this code. 
Then just: python pi.py

Setting up PyGame
---------------------------------

OSX & WINDOWS:
The tar file is for OSX, the zip is for Windows.
Install intructions are here:
http://www.pygame.org/download.shtml

